serviceDescription.author: 권필
serviceDescription.explanation: 국내 : poi_db_p 사용 (LOD적용) 국외는 NE, OSM 혼용, 김포철도추가

poi_db_p.description: 국가명 뺍니다 and dp_code not in ('011700','011701')

levelSet.extractQuery: select 'mid' as type, mid, mid as id, cid, lv_min, lv_max, dp_code, dp_flag, name_full, name_dp, name_dp_1, name_dp_2, name_dp_3, name_dp_ml, eng, chn, jpn, dp_angle, rank_11, rank_12, rank_13, rank_14, rank_15, rank_16, rank_17, rank_18, rank_19, editcode, score as rank, ST_AsBinary(shape) as geom from poi_db_p_lod_web_test where ${intersects} and (editcode is null or editcode not in ('D')) and dp_code not in ('011700','011701')

select 'ne_id' as type, cast(ne_id as text) as id, scalerank, labelrank, level, name, name_long, abbrev, formal_en, name_alt, pop_rank, pop_est as rank, min_zoom, adm0_a3 as iso_country_code, tiny, coalesce(name_ko, name_en, name) as name, coalesce(name_ko, name) as name_ko, coalesce(name_ja, name) as name_ja, coalesce(name_en, name) as name_en, coalesce(name_zh, name) as name_zh, ${shape} from ne_country where ${intersects} and featurecla = 'Admin-0 country'

select 'ne_id' as type, cast(ne_id as text) as id, name_alt, datarank, abbrev, adm0_a3, adm0_label, min_label, cast(min_zoom as float) as min_zoom, name_en, adm0_a3 as iso_country_code, coalesce(case when name_ko like '%시' or name_ko like '%현' or name_ko like '%주' or name_ko like '%성' or name_ko like '%구'                     or name_ko like '% 시' or name_ko like '% 현' or name_ko like '% 주' or name_ko like '% 성' or name_ko like '% 구'            then trim(left(name_ko, -1)) else name_ko end, name_en, name) as name, coalesce(case when name_ko like '%시' or name_ko like '%현' or name_ko like '%주' or name_ko like '%성' or name_ko like '%구'                     or name_ko like '% 시' or name_ko like '% 현' or name_ko like '% 주' or name_ko like '% 성' or name_ko like '% 구'            then trim(left(name_ko, -1)) else name_ko end, name) as name_ko,            coalesce(case when name_ja like '%州' or name_ja like '%県' then trim(left(name_ja, -1)) else name_ja end, name) as name_ja, coalesce(name_en, name) as name_en, coalesce(name_zh, name) as name_zh, ${shape} from ne_admin where ${intersects}

visibleRange.filter: min_zoom <= 7.8 and adm0_a3 not in ('IOA') or adm0_a3 in ('PRK')

city.description: ne_id 는 unique합니다.Low Level은 ne_id, High Level은 osm_id를 사용해요

levelSet.description: 이곳은 natural earth 를 이용해서 만든 도시 POI입니다.
levelSet.extractQuery:
select 'ne_id' as type, cast(ne_id as text) as id, ne_id, featurecla, pop_max as population, cast(pop_max as int) as pop,  cast(pop_max as int) as rank, scalerank, featurecla, cast(worldcity as int) as worldcity, cast(megacity as int) as megacity, pop_max, rank_max, min_zoom, adm0_a3 as iso_country_code,
            coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right(name_ko, 1) = '시' or right(name_ko, 1) = '군'            then left(name_ko, -1) else name_ko end, '특별', ''), '특급', ''), '직할',''), ' 시', ''), ' 현' , ''), ' 구', ''), name_en, name) as name,
            coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right(name_ko, 1) = '시' or right(name_ko, 1) = '군'           then left(name_ko, -1) else name_ko end, '특별', ''), '특급', ''), '직할',''), ' 시', ''), ' 현' , ''), ' 구', ''), name) as name_ko,
             coalesce(case when right(name_ja, 1) = '市' or right(name_ja, 1) = '郡' then left(name_ja, -1) else name_ja end, name) as name_ja,
             coalesce(name_en, name) as name_en,
             coalesce(name_zh, name) as name_zh,

             ${shape} from ne_city where ${intersects} and adm0_a3 not in ('KOR','PRK') or (adm0_a3 = 'PRK' and name_ko is not null)

levelSet.description: 이곳은 OSMPOI를 이용해서 만든 도시 입니다
levelSet.extractQuery:
select 'osm_id' as type, cast(osm_id as text) as id,'osm' as data, cast(category as int) as category, osm_id, place, '' as featurecla, capital, cast(pop as int) as population, cast(pop as int) as pop, cast(pop as int) as rank, null as scalerank, null as worldcity, null as megacity, null as iso_country_code, cast(pop as int) as pop_max, null as rank_max, null as min_zoom,

            coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right("name:ko", 1) = '시' or right("name:ko", 1) = '군'
           then left("name:ko", -1) else "name:ko" end, ' 향', ''), ' 구', ''), ' 주', ''), ' 진', ''), "name:en", name) as name,            coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right("name:ko", 1) = '시' or right("name:ko", 1) = '군'           then left("name:ko", -1) else "name:ko" end, ' 향', ''), ' 구', ''), ' 주', ''), ' 진', ''), name) as name_ko,            coalesce(case when right("name:ja", 1) = '市' or right("name:ja", 1) = '郡' or right ("name:ja", 1) = '県' or right ("name:ja", 1) = '州'           then left("name:ja", -1) else "name:ja" end, name) as name_ja,            coalesce("name:en", name) as name_en,            coalesce("name:zh", name) as name_zh,            ${shape} from osm_poi_cities where ${intersects} and category in (4,11) and name not like ('%区') and category not in (1,2)

levelSet.description: 이곳은 OSMPOI를 이용해서 만든 도시 입니다
levelSet.extractQuery:
select 'osm_id' as type, cast(osm_id as text) as id, 'osm' as data, cast(category as int) as category, osm_id, place, '' as featurecla, capital, cast(pop as int) as population, cast(pop as int) as pop, cast(pop as int) as rank,      null as scalerank, null as worldcity, null as megacity, null as iso_country_code, cast(pop as int) as pop_max, null as rank_max, null as min_zoom,

            coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right("name:ko", 1) = '시' or right("name:ko", 1) = '군'
           then left("name:ko", -1) else "name:ko" end, ' 향', ''), ' 구', ''), ' 주', ''), ' 진', ''), "name:en", name) as name,

             coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right("name:ko", 1) = '시' or right("name:ko", 1) = '군'
           then left("name:ko", -1) else "name:ko" end, ' 향', ''), ' 구', ''), ' 주', ''), ' 진', ''), name) as name_ko,

            coalesce(case when right("name:ja", 1) = '市' or right("name:ja", 1) = '郡' or right ("name:ja", 1) = '県' or right ("name:ja", 1) = '州'
           then left("name:ja", -1) else "name:ja" end, name) as name_ja,
            coalesce("name:en", name) as name_en,
            coalesce("name:zh", name) as name_zh,

              ${shape} from osm_poi_cities where ${intersects} and category in (4,5,6,7,8,11,12,13)

levelSet.description: 이곳은 OSMPOI를 이용해서 만든 도시 입니다
levelSet.extractQuery:
select 'osm_id' as type, cast(osm_id as text) as id, 'osm' as data, cast(category as int) as category, osm_id, place, '' as featurecla, capital, cast(pop as int) as population, cast(pop as int) as pop, cast(pop as int) as rank,     null as scalerank, null as worldcity, null as megacity, null as iso_country_code, cast(pop as int) as pop_max, null as rank_max, null as min_zoom,

            coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right("name:ko", 1) = '시' or right("name:ko", 1) = '군'
           then left("name:ko", -1) else "name:ko" end, ' 향', ''), ' 구', ''), ' 주', ''), ' 진', ''), "name:en", name) as name,

           coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right("name:ko", 1) = '시' or right("name:ko", 1) = '군'
           then left("name:ko", -1) else "name:ko" end, ' 향', ''), ' 구', ''), ' 주', ''), ' 진', ''), name) as name_ko,

            coalesce(case when right("name:ja", 1) = '市' or right("name:ja", 1) = '郡' or right ("name:ja", 1) = '県' or right ("name:ja", 1) = '州'
           then left("name:ja", -1) else "name:ja" end, name) as name_ja,
            coalesce("name:en", name) as name_en,
            coalesce("name:zh", name) as name_zh,


            ${shape} from osm_poi_cities where ${intersects} and category in (4,5,8,11,12,13) or (category in (6,7) and pop is not null)

levelSet.description: 이곳은 OSMPOI를 이용해서 만든 도시 입니다
levelSet.extractQuery:
select 'osm_id' as type, cast(osm_id as text) as id, 'osm' as data, cast(category as int) as category, osm_id, place, '' as featurecla, capital, cast(pop as int) as population, cast(pop as int) as pop, cast(pop as int) as rank,     null as scalerank, null as worldcity, null as megacity, null as iso_country_code, cast(pop as int) as pop_max, null as rank_max, null as min_zoom,

            coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right("name:ko", 1) = '시' or right("name:ko", 1) = '군'
           then left("name:ko", -1) else "name:ko" end, ' 향', ''), ' 구', ''), ' 주', ''), ' 진', ''), "name:en", name) as name,

           coalesce(replace(replace(replace(replace(case when right("name:ko", 1) = '시' or right("name:ko", 1) = '군'
           then left("name:ko", -1) else "name:ko" end, ' 향', ''), ' 구', ''), ' 주', ''), ' 진', ''), name) as name_ko,

            coalesce(case when right("name:ja", 1) = '市' or right("name:ja", 1) = '郡' or right ("name:ja", 1) = '県' or right ("name:ja", 1) = '州'
           then left("name:ja", -1) else "name:ja" end, name) as name_ja,
            coalesce("name:en", name) as name_en,
            coalesce("name:zh", name) as name_zh,


            ${shape} from osm_poi_cities where ${intersects} and category in (4,5,6,7,8,11,12,13)

select 'osm_id' as type, cast(osm_way_id as text) as id, osm_way_id, coalesce("name:ko", "name:en", name) as name, type as type2, iata, alt_name, religion, area, coalesce("name:ko", name) as name_ko, coalesce("name:ja", name) as name_ja, coalesce("name:en", name) as name_en, coalesce("name:zh", name) as name_zh, ${shape} from osm_polygon_poi where ${intersects} and name not like ('%위대한 수령%') and name not like ('%령도자%') and name not like ('%동지%') and name not like ('%수령%') and name not like ('위대한')
select 'place' as type, nsid as id, mid, nsid, cid, dp_code,name_dp_1,name_dp_2,name_dp_3,name_dp,name_dp_ml,dp_angle,rank_map,event,${shape} from "k5_poi_event_p"  where  ${intersects}
select mid,dp_lv14,dp_code,name_dp,${shape} from "k5_na_poi_db_p"  where  ${intersects} and DP_LV14 in (1,2)

deletedMids.description: place 삭제된 POI 목록(deletedMids.csv) 기반으로 지도 화면 미노출 처리, exclude - 삭제 대상 POI 목록 중 예외처리 할 mid 목록

categoryCode.description: 지도 화면은 노출 되지만, clickable 하지 않도록 mid - sid 매핑 제외 처리, exclude - 매핑 제외 처리할 categoryCode 목록

representativeStation.description: 지하철 환승역 대표 mid 매핑 [ 대표 MID : 환승역 MID ]
